item.title: Personal Life
item.description: Meet my adorable parrotlet Smurf. He is a two year old boy and he can say a few words, such as “Peekaboo”, “Birdie Birdie”, and “Pikachu”. Smurf loves hemp seeds and millet sprays. This is my female canary, and she is stealing Smurf’s hemp seeds.
